data.description: Adorable 3/2 in the desirable Westwind neighborhood of Elgin. It has wonderful layout with open living, kitchen and formal dining area.  Master is complete with walk-in closet and private bath with double vanity. 3rd bedroom is an ideal home office or guest bath.  Separate laundry room/mudroom connects clean 2 car garage.  Low HOA with a community playground and park.  Home has a new roof but is sold as-is.  The home has good bones and needs some repair to kitchen sink plumbing, new fence, new carpet and bathroom flooring.  Foundation repairs completed and lifetime warranty transfers to new owners.  Refrigerator, washer/dryer negotiable.
